criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  being treated with glucocorticoids (5 mg of prednisone equivalents) for the preceding
             3 months or less, and expect to continue the therapy for at least 12 months;

          -  being post-menopausal;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  use of other steroids or osteoporosis medications;

          -  have been diagnosed with metabolic bone diseases (other than glucocorticoid
             osteoporosis)

          -  previous (1 year) or current use of HRT (hormone replacement therapy)

          -  other diseases that may affect participation (i.e. mental illness)
